  "name": "Twenty (CRM maintained)",
  "description": "Maintained-in-repo Twenty CRM plugin for OpenClaw (plugins/twenty-plugin). Vendored from @lacneu/twenty-openclaw@0.8.4 with absorbed metadata-envelope compatibility and empty-write safety guards. Manages people / companies / opportunities / notes / tasks, models custom objects + fields via the Metadata API, dashboards, and workflows, gated by workspace whitelist and approval prompts. The plugin id is kept as `twenty-openclaw` so existing openclaw.json config, tool names, and skills continue to work unchanged.",
